NAME
        shoot - shoot a missile at a target

SYNOPSIS
        shoot at <target> [in] [the] [<body location>] [<remote room>]

DESCRIPTION
        You can shoot a missile at a target. This skill requires a
        missile weapon and appropriate projectile. The success is
        determined with your missile skill compared with the target's
        defensive skills and stats.

        If you try to kill someone you know, i.e., have been introduced
        to and/or remember you will have to confirm your kill command
        by typing it twice unless you use the persons name.

SEE ALSO
        fire, shoot, select, kill
